        "subject": "LU-2059 llog: MGC to use OSD API for backup logs",
        "message": "LU-2059 llog: MGC to use OSD API for backup logs\n\nMGC uses lvfs API to access local llogs blocking removal of old code\n\n- MGS is converted to use OSD API for local llogs\n- llog_is_empty() and llog_backup() are introduced\n- initial OSD start initialize run ctxt so llog can use it too\n- replay-ost-single determines config log size for better estimation\n\nSigned-off-by: Mikhail Pershin <mike.pershin@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I021ed8191b86727375aa9dc7f3a8760c89dd2e6e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
